<plot>The three horror tales in The Edge of Reality are "Dead Man", "The Maze", and "The Quarry". The first story Dead Man is based on a short story in the tradition of Edgar Allen Poe's The Tell-Tale Heart. It's about a dead man who won't rest until he exposes his killer. The second story The Maze is about a man who faces his own worst enemy, himself! The third story called The Quarry is about two men on a camping trip who have an encounter with the legendary Bigfoot!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?554874</url></doc>
